sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles' import { Card, CardContent, Typography } from '@material-ui/core' import { commonStyles, desktopStyles, mobileStyles, TabStyles } from './styles' import Link from 'next/link' const useStyles = makeStyles(theme => ({ ...commonStyles, [theme.breakpoints.up('xl')]: desktopStyles, [theme.breakpoints.between('xs', 'md')]: TabStyles, [theme.breakpoints.down('xs')]: mobileStyles })) const EventIconCard = ({data}) => { const classes = useStyles() return ( {data.title} ) } export default EventIconCard
